Groove 68Swing

Drum-Snare  Sequence  *  *  {1 0 90 * 6} {1 0 90}
Drum-Kick   Sequence  *  *  *  {1 0 90}
Drum-HH     Sequence  *  *  *  {1 0 60; 4 0 40 }
Walk        Sequence  *  *  {1 4 90; 3 8 80; 4 4 70; 6 8 50} {1 2 90}
/// Chord     

DefGroove 68SwingIntro   Basic 4 bar introduction.


