//// Ending

Groove 68Swing
Seqsize 2

Drum-Snare  Sequence  {1 0 90 * 6} {1 0 90}
Drum-Kick   Sequence  {1 0 90}
Drum-HH     Sequence  {1 0 60 * 6} {1 0 100}
Walk        Sequence  {1 4. 90; 4. 2 70} {1 2 90}
